Yandex,is,the,largest,search,engine,in,Russia,and,develops,a,number,of,Internet,based,services,and,products,Yandex,offers,owners,of,websites,and,blogs,tools,with,which,they,can,apply,the,functional,services,of,Yandex,in,their,projects,The,Yandex,Direct,API,allows,developers,to,create,applications,which,directly,interact,with,the,Yandex,contextual,advertising,service,These,applications,allow,advertising,agencies,as,well,as,direct,advertisers,to,run,complex,large,scaled,advertising,campaigns,It,uses,SOAP,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON